<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189025>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 30. Figs. 24 – 26, Oxyethira tamandua, n. sp., male genitalia: 24: dorsal, 25: ventral, 26: lateral. Figs. 27 – 30, Oxyethira poapi, n. sp., male genitalia: 27: ventral, 28: lateral. 29 – 30. Phallus: 29: dorsal, 30: lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189025/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.189026>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 43. Figs. 31, 36, Alisotrichia cainguas, n. sp.: 31: adult, lateral. 36: male genitalia. Figs. 32, 37, Ochrotrichia pora, n. sp.: 32: adult, ventral. 37: male genitalia. Figs. 33, 38, Paratrichia acuti, n. sp.: 33: adult, lateral. 38: male genitalia. Figs. 34, 40, Rhyacopsyche garuhape, n. sp.: 34: adult, ventral. 40: male genitalia. Figs. 35, 39, 41, Oxyethira tamandua, n. sp.: 35: adult, ventral. 39: male genitalia, dorsal. 41: male genitalia, lateral. Figs. 42, 43, Oxyethira poapi, n. sp., male genitalia: 42: lateral. 43: phallus apex, detail." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/189026/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

